name: GameFi Protocol
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: GameFi Protocol is the first GameFi mining pool protocol, aiming to build the first global Gamefi aggregation platform, and its governance token is GFI. The holders of this token spontaneously form GFP-DAO. Conduct community governance of GameFi Protocol.
